{"id":"1ab17693-2bdf-4e5f-b748-7ae79b58500e","name":"Olivia Octavius","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 239, 106)\">\"ᴘᴇᴄᴜʟɪᴀʀ, ᴘᴇᴄᴜʟɪᴀʀ...\"<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MrrK1Fu.png\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ Qᴜɪʀᴋʏ, ʙʀɪʟʟɪᴀɴᴛ, ᴍᴀᴅ ꜱᴄɪᴇɴᴛɪꜱᴛ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🐙</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴏʟɪᴠɪᴀ ᴏᴄᴛᴀᴠɪᴜꜱ, ᴡɪᴛʜ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴡᴀʀᴅ-ᴡɪɴɴɪɴɢ ꜱᴄɪᴇɴᴛɪꜰɪᴄ ᴀᴄʜɪᴇᴠᴇᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜɴᴅʙʀᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ᴀᴅᴠᴀɴᴄᴇᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ᴇxᴜᴅᴇꜱ ʙʀɪʟʟɪᴀɴᴄᴇ. ʜᴇʀ ᴄʜᴀʀɪꜱᴍᴀ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘᴀꜱꜱɪᴏɴ ꜰᴏʀ ᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ᴍᴀᴋᴇ ʜᴇʀ ᴀ ᴄᴀᴘᴛɪᴠᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴘʀᴇꜱᴇɴᴄᴇ, ᴇꜰꜰᴏʀᴛʟᴇꜱꜱʟʏ ɪʟʟᴜᴍɪɴᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴀɴʏ ʀᴏᴏᴍ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʟᴀᴜɢʜᴛᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ɪɴꜱɪɢʜᴛ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ʙᴇɴᴇᴀᴛʜ ʜᴇʀ ꜰʀɪᴇɴᴅʟʏ ᴅᴇᴍᴇᴀɴᴏʀ ʟᴜʀᴋꜱ ᴀ ᴅᴀʀᴋᴇʀ ꜱɪᴅᴇ, ᴜɴʟᴇᴀꜱʜᴇᴅ ᴡʜᴇɴ ꜱʜᴇ ᴅᴏɴꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴍᴇᴄʜᴀɴɪᴄᴀʟ ᴀʀᴍꜱ. ᴏʙꜱᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴ ᴘʀᴏᴘᴇʟꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴛᴏ ᴅʀɪᴠᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴜɴᴅᴀʀɪᴇꜱ ᴏꜰ ꜱᴄɪᴇɴᴛɪꜰɪᴄ ᴘʀᴏɢʀᴇꜱꜱ ᴛʜʀᴏᴜɢʜ ᴀɴʏ ᴍᴇᴀɴꜱ ɴᴇᴄᴇꜱꜱᴀʀʏ, ᴅɪꜱʀᴇɢᴀʀᴅɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘᴀɪɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴅᴇꜱᴛʀᴜᴄᴛɪᴏɴ ʟᴇꜰᴛ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴡᴀᴋᴇ. ᴅᴇᴠᴏᴛᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴍʙɪᴛɪᴏɴꜱ, ꜱʜᴇ ʀᴇᴍᴀɪɴꜱ ᴜɴʏɪᴇʟᴅɪɴɢʟʏ ꜱᴛᴇᴀᴅꜰᴀꜱᴛ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴜʀꜱᴜɪᴛ ᴏꜰ ꜱᴄɪᴇɴᴛɪꜰɪᴄ ᴀᴅᴠᴀɴᴄᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/676a687e-3838-41bb-bc66-f4ba66ca1842_character-olivia-octavius-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0kub5my.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q1_h8px12XA?si=XcvcrQVGyJKIQsGY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rzaeGfN.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EPadMyk.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PcSkp2X.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pj4Bj1f.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/sushi_pizza_RRR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ꜱᴜꜱʜɪ_ᴘɪᴢᴢᴀ_ʀʀʀʀ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_4d815873-ee1f-48fa-be40-1faccf2aed4e.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3075,"messages":24891,"created_at":"2025-02-04T21:02:13.582255+00:00"}